{"tid":2433764,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"［百屌成材］sony手機回歸自家Sony客戶服務中心保養！","createTime":"2021-03-05T05:55:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T12:43:24.000Z","uid":10717,"like":35,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"36311d6cbcfb21281a16043e7c5746fb3d4ff182","tid":2433764,"uid":10717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T05:55:20.000Z","msg":"親愛的顧客：<br />\n<br />\n多謝您對Sony 產品的支持。<br />\n<br />\n由2021年3月15日起，銅鑼灣Sony客戶服務中心將會提供 Xperia產品的維修保養及售後服務，並同時備有專遞維修服務供選擇。<br />\n<br />\n而位於旺角銀城廣場之Sony Xperia客戶服務中心，則於2021年3月15日停止上述服務。<br />\n<br />\nSony客戶服務中心地址及服務時間、專遞維修服務網址如下：<br />\n地址<br />\n香港銅鑼灣軒尼詩道555號東角中心(舊翼)16樓<br />\n服務時間<br />\n星期一至日上午十一時至晚上八時<br />\n<br />\n專遞維修服務<br />\n網址<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sony.com.hk/service/repair/zh/index.do\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sony.com.hk%2Fservice%2Frepair%2Fzh%2Findex.do&d=eRHmMhW6fCYgFX7Mu85bUrXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=e3352cc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sony.com.hk/service/repair/zh/index.do</a><br />\n<br />\n有關Sony Xperia客戶服務的詳情，請瀏覽Sony Mobile HK Facebook專頁或致電服務熱線：8203-8863。<br />\n<br />\n索尼香港<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9e6f47956796e2a51f0509390798abd3c3c901f","tid":2433764,"uid":213607,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T05:57:03.000Z","msg":"10年死忠 會都轉左幾年<br />\n賣得貴過iphone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d03aa15fd2b47f574b0697229540ef344b503c96","tid":2433764,"uid":653,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T05:59:31.000Z","msg":"屌佢比銀城做臭曬先收返黎做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4125cce09af354d46fa1d6f07b859a5ef5c73f56","tid":2433764,"uid":8410,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T0